hadiths[9]{hadithnumber,text}:
2508,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni zirah jau ke badley girwii rakhi thi. aik din main khud aap ke paas jau ki roti aur baasii charbi lekar hazir hua tha. maine khud Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they ke aal Muhammad par koi subah aur koi Sham aisi nahi aai ke aik saa se zyada kuchh aur maujood raha ho, halanke aap ke nau (9) ghar they."
2509,ham ne Ibrahim Nakhai (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ke yahan qarz mein rahan aur zaamin ka zikr kya to unhon-ne kaha ke ham se Aswad ne bayan kya aur unse Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik Yahudi se ghalla khareedaa aik muqarrara muddat ke qarz par aur apni zirah uske yahan girwii rakhi thi.
2510,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Kab-bin-Ashraf (yahoodii, Islam ka pakka dushman) ka kaam kon tamam karega ke usne Allah aur uske rasool ko bahut takleef de rakhi hai. Muhammad-bin-Musallema (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main (ye khidmat anjam doonga). chunanche wo uske paas gaey aur kaha ke aik ya 2 wasq ghalla qarz leney ke iraadey se aaya hun. Kab ne kaha lekin tumhen apni beeviyon ko mere yahan girwii rakhna hoga Muhammad-bin-Musallema aur uske sathiyon ne kaha ke ham apni beeviyon ko tumharey paas kis tarah girwii rakh saktey hain jabke tum sarey Arab mein khoobsurat ho. usne kaha ke phir apni aulad girwii rakh do. unhon-ne kaha ke ham apni aulad kis tarah rahan rakh saktey hain isi par unhein gali di jaya karegi ke aik 2 wasq ghalley ke liye rahan rakh diye gaey they, to hamarey liye badi sharm ki baat hogi. albatta ham apne hathiyar tumharey yahan rahan rakh saktey hain. Sufiyan ne kaha ke lafz ( لأمة ( se murad hathiyar hain. phir Muhammad-bin-Musalema (Raziallahu anhu) us se dobara milney ka wada karke (chaley aaey aur raat ko iske yahan pahunch kar) usey qatl kar diya. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khabar di."
2511,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya girwii janwar par uska kharch nikalney ke liye sawari ki jaey, doodh wala janwar girwii ho to uska doodh piyaa jaey."
2512,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, girwii janwar par uske kharch ke badal sawari ki jaey. isi tarah doodh waley janwar ka jab wo girwii ho to kharch ke badal uska doodh piyaa jaey aur jo koi sawari karey ya doodh piey wahi uska kharch uthaaey."
2513,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kuchh muddat thehra kar aik Yahudi se ghalla khareedaa aur apni zirah uske paas girwii rakhii.
2514,maine Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein (2 aurton ke muqaddime mein) likha to uske jawab mein unhon-ne tahreer farmaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne faisla kya tha ke (agar muddaii gawah na pesh kar sakey) to mudduaa alaih se qism li jaeygi.
2515,jo shakhs jaan-bojh kar us niyat se jhooti qism khaaey ke is tarah doosrey ke maal par apni milkiyat jamaaey to wo Allah Taala se us haal mein milega ke Allah Taala is par ghazabnaak hoga. us irshad ki tasdeeq mein Allah Taala ne (sura aale-Imraan mein) ye aayat nazil farmai ( إن الذين يشترون بعهد الله وأيمانهم ثمنا قليلا‏ ( ''wo log jo Allah ke ahad aur apni qasmon ke zariey duniya ki thodi poojii khareedtey hain'' aakhir aayat tak unhon-ne tilawat ki. abu-Waaeil ne kaha iske baad asha's-bin-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey ghar tashrif laey aur puchha ke abu-Abdur-Rehman (abu-Masood (rz)) ne tum se kon si hadis bayan ki hai? unhon-ne kaha ke ham ne uper wali hadis unke samney pesh kar di. is par unhon-ne kaha ke unhon-ne sach bayan kya hai. mera aik (yahoodii) shakhs se kuwein ke mamley mein jhagdaa hua tha. ham apna jhagdaa lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum apne gawah lao warna doosrey fareeq se qism li jaeygi. maine arz kya phir ye to qism kha lega aur (jhoot bolney par) usey kuchh parwah na hogi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo shakhs jaan-bojh kar kisi ka maal hadap karne ke liye jhooti qism khaaey to Allah Taala se wo us haal mein milega ke wo is par bahut hi zyada ghazabnaak hoga. Allah Taala ne uski tasdeeq mein ye aayat nazil ki. iske baad unhon-ne wahi aayat padhi ( إن الذين يشترون بعهد الله وأيمانهم ثمنا قليلا‏ ( ''jo log Allah ke ahad aur apni qasmon ke zariey thodi poojii khareedtey hain''. aakhir tak.
2516,jo shakhs jaan-bojh kar us niyat se jhooti qism khaaey ke is tarah doosrey ke maal par apni milkiyat jamaaey to wo Allah Taala se us haal mein milega ke Allah Taala is par ghazabnaak hoga. us irshad ki tasdeeq mein Allah Taala ne (sura aale-Imraan mein) ye aayat nazil farmai ( إن الذين يشترون بعهد الله وأيمانهم ثمنا قليلا‏ ( ''wo log jo Allah ke ahad aur apni qasmon ke zariey duniya ki thodi poojii khareedtey hain'' aakhir aayat tak unhon-ne tilawat ki. abu-Waaeil ne kaha iske baad asha's-bin-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey ghar tashrif laey aur puchha ke abu-Abdur-Rehman (abu-Masood (rz)) ne tum se kon si hadis bayan ki hai? unhon-ne kaha ke ham ne uper wali hadis unke samney pesh kar di. is par unhon-ne kaha ke unhon-ne sach bayan kya hai. mera aik (yahoodii) shakhs se kuwein ke mamley mein jhagdaa hua tha. ham apna jhagdaa lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum apne gawah lao warna doosrey fareeq se qism li jaeygi. maine arz kya phir ye to qism kha lega aur (jhoot bolney par) usey kuchh parwah na hogi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo shakhs jaan-bojh kar kisi ka maal hadap karne ke liye jhooti qism khaaey to Allah Taala se wo us haal mein milega ke wo is par bahut hi zyada ghazabnaak hoga. Allah Taala ne uski tasdeeq mein ye aayat nazil ki. iske baad unhon-ne wahi aayat padhi ( إن الذين يشترون بعهد الله وأيمانهم ثمنا قليلا‏ ( ''jo log Allah ke ahad aur apni qasmon ke zariey thodi poojii khareedtey hain''. aakhir tak.
